Method: add_bone_weight(vertex_index: int, bone_index: int, weight: float)
Adds a bone weight to a vertex.

Method: remove_bone_weight(vertex_index: int, bone_index: int)
Removes a bone weight from a vertex.

Method: clear_bones()
Removes all bones from the mesh.

Method: commit_to_surface(mesh: Mesh, surface_index: int) → Error
Commits the modified mesh data back to a surface of a Mesh. Returns an Error code.

Method: clear()
Clears the MeshDataTool, freeing its resources.

